@node "Document_0" "Program and Distribution Notes"
@{b}Program and distribution notes@{ub}

RelVel is (C) 1997 by Brian Savage and it is freely distributable as long as
all of its files are included in their original form without additions,
deletions, or modifications of any kind, and only a nominal fee is charged
for its distribution.

RelVel is EmailWare and as such is completely FREE!  All I ask is that if you
like RelVel and find it useful, please send me an @{"email" link "Document_4" 0} to tell me so. In the
email please give your real name and the country in which you live.

Permission is required by the author for inclusion of RelVel on magazine
